There’s a lovely quote in the aforementioned documentary from a young gay guy: “I love my gay voice.
Of course, not all gay guys have gay voice and not all guys with gay voice are gay.
profiles at least one self-identified straight guy who is often mistaken for gay because of the sound of his voice.
It is not true that if he has gay voice, then he must only sleep with men.
For as much as a gay voice can be a blessing, it can also put an immediate target on its owner as soon as he opens his mouth and attempts to function in the world as anyone would.